Class Element

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Element
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IElement
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MobileElement, StaticElement

    public class Element
extends Object
implements IElement
    The Element class introduces elements based on 3 criteria : An x and y coordinates to locate on a map at the start of the game. A url to connect the various images format . png. And a list to give him a permeability.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Corentin Devrouete
